minimized</span></font><font size="-1"
 style="font-family: helvetica,arial,sans-serif;"><br>
&#8220;Minimized&#8221; will generate a more
compact tree which could
have an impact on the transparency.</font><br
 style="font-family: helvetica,arial,sans-serif;">
