&nbsp;<br>
<br>
Once a tree diagram is generated, it is not possible to add processes,
actors, stores or flows. (The tool bar is active, but trying to add new
model elements will be refused.)<br>
&nbsp;<br>
A tree diagram is linked with its original diagram (see the Parent
Diagram field in the design panel), so modifications of its processes
will be displayed instantaneously, but if you change the parent diagram
by adding new subprocesses, the tree diagram is not updated
automatically.&nbsp; To update the tree diagram select the Tree Diagram
in the explorer, and choose Generate-&gt;Process Tree.<br>
